{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Server-sent events","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events\">Server-sent events</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Guides</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events/Using_server-sent_events\">Using server-sent events</a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Interfaces</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/EventSource\"><code>EventSource</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>전통적으로 웹페이지는 새로운 데이터를 받기 위해 서버로 요청을 보내야만 합니다; 서버로 데이터를 요청하는 방식입니다. 하지만 Server-Sent Events 방식으로 웹페이지의 요청 없이도 언제든지 서버가 새로운 데이터를 보내는 것이 가능합니다. 이렇게 보내진 메시지는 웹페이지 안에서 <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event\">Events</a> + 데이터</em>로 다룰 수 있습니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"기본_사용하기","title":"기본 &amp; 사용하기","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Server-Sent Events를 배우려면 다음 글을 읽어보세요: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events/Using_server-sent_events\">Server-Sent Events 사용하기</a>.</p>","titleAsText":"기본 & 사용하기"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"interfaces","title":"인터페이스","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"eventsource\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/EventSource\"><code>EventSource</code></a></dt>\n <dd>서버와의 연결, 이벤트/데이터, 에러 받아오기, 연결 종료하기 등을 다루는 모든 기능을 정의하고 있습니다.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"예제","title":"예제","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/dom-examples/tree/master/server-sent-events\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">PHP를 이용하여 구현한 간단한 SSE 데모</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"명세","title":"명세","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#server-sent-events\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ko\">The definition of 'Server-sent events' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"더 찾아보기","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"tools","title":"도구","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://github.com/EventSource/eventsource\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Node.js를 위한 EventSource 폴리필</a></li>\n <li>Remy Sharp의 <a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://github.com/remy/polyfills/blob/master/EventSource.js\" rel=\" noopener\">EventSource 폴리필</a></li>\n <li>Yaffle의 <a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://github.com/Yaffle/EventSource\" rel=\" noopener\">EventSource 폴리필</a></li>\n <li>Rick Waldron <a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://github.com/rwldrn/jquery.eventsource\" rel=\" noopener\">jquery 플러그인</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://intercoolerjs.org/docs.html#sse\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">선언적인 SSE를 지원하는 </a>intercooler.js</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"related_topics","title":"관련 주제","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/AJAX\" title=\"AJAX\">AJAX</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript\" title=\"JavaScript\">JavaScript</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSockets_API\" title=\"WebSockets\">WebSockets</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"그_외_자료","title":"그 외 자료","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>SSE로 구현된 <a href=\"https://hacks.mozilla.org/2011/06/a-wall-powered-by-eventsource-and-server-sent-events/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Twitter 어플리케이션</a>과 <a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://github.com/mozilla/webowonder-demos/tree/master/demos/friends%20timeline\" rel=\" noopener\">깃허브에 공개된 소스코드</a>.</li>\n <li><a href=\"https://dsheiko.com/weblog/html5-and-server-sent-events\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5와 Server-sent events</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://rajudasa.blogspot.in/2012/05/html5-server-sent-events-using-aspnet.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Asp.net을 이용한 Server-Sent Events</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"기본 &amp; 사용하기","id":"기본_사용하기"},{"text":"인터페이스","id":"interfaces"},{"text":"예제","id":"예제"},{"text":"명세","id":"명세"},{"text":"더 찾아보기","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"전통적으로 웹페이지는 새로운 데이터를 받기 위해 서버로 요청을 보내야만 합니다; 서버로 데이터를 요청하는 방식입니다. 하지만 Server-Sent Events 방식으로 웹페이지의 요청 없이도 언제든지 서버가 새로운 데이터를 보내는 것이 가능합니다. 이렇게 보내진 메시지는 웹페이지 안에서 Events + 데이터로 다룰 수 있습니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"サーバー送信イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/api/server-sent_events","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/api/server-sent_events/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events","title":"Server-sent events"}],"pageTitle":"Server-sent events - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}